snippet.title: The Grinch game trailer
snippet.description:
Now that I finally own the DVD of "How the Grinch stole Christmas" from 2000, I properly recorded the video game tie-in trailer.

I found it on the bonus features and since I was obsessed with it when I was a kid, what better reason and time to share it by uploading it on December? 😝 More so when the year 2020 is one of the worst years ever. This at least will serve as nostalgia trip.
